for i in range(int(input())):
    s,sg,fg,d,t = [int(i) for i in input().split()]
    dis = (d*50)
    speed = dis/t 
    exs = (speed*18)/5
    ts = s + exs
    ss = abs(sg-ts)
    sf = abs(fg-ts)
    if ss>sf:
        print('FATHER')
    elif ss<sf:
        print('SEBI')
    elif ss==sf:
        print('DRAW')

# cook your dish here
from sys import stdin, stdout
ans = []

for _ in range(int(stdin.readline())):
    spd, sg, fg, d, time = map(int, stdin.readline().split())
    ckh = ((d*180)/time) + spd
    dsg = abs(ckh - sg)
    dfg = abs(ckh - fg)
    ans.append('DRAW' if dsg == dfg else 'SEBI' if dsg < dfg else 'FATHER')
stdout.write('\n'.join(ans))
